## Limitations

The findings in this report are based on available online resources and may not encompass all aspects of how crime affects individuals. The impact of crime can vary significantly depending on the type of crime, the individual's personal circumstances, and the support systems available to them. Additionally, the data may not reflect recent trends or changes in crime patterns and their effects on individuals. Further research, including empirical studies and interviews with crime victims, would provide a more in-depth understanding of the issue.